@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos(v1)
    tmp = ((v1 / (v0 + 0.61 + v2 + 0.66)) / wp.sin((v1 + 0.17 * v2 + 0.62)))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.abs(wp.abs(tmp + 0.24)))
    tmp = 0.91
    data[tid] = v0
